<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.8.4">
<l>mañcuyar māmaṇik kuṉṟamēnti māmaḻai kāttoru māyavāṉai</l>
<l>yañcava taṉmarup poṉṟuvāṅku māyarkol māyama ṟiyamāṭṭēṉ</l>
<l>veñcuṭa rāḻiyuñ caṅkumēnti vētamu ṉōtuvar nītivāṉat</l>
<l>tañcuṭar pōṉṟiva rārkkoleṉṉa</l>
<l>vaṭṭapu yakarat tēṉeṉṟārē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Is [he] the cowherd who, having warded off the great rain,</l>
<l rend="indent">lifting a great, high, misty, sapphire[-like] mountain,</l>
<l>Once took a tusk so that a dark elephant was terrified?</l>
<l rend="indent">I am not able to understand [this] illusion.</l>
<l>When I asked, “Who is this appearing [as] the lovely sun in the sky,</l>
<l rend="indent">bearing the conch and the discus [like] the burning sun,</l>
<l>The righteousness of those who chant the Vedas in front [of me]?”</l>
<l rend="indent">he answered, “I am he in the house of the eight-armed [lord].”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
